# CODEOWNERS — drives auto-requested PR reviews and, if branch
# protection is configured with "Require review from Code Owners",
# gates merge until at least one listed owner approves.
#
# Patterns are evaluated bottom-to-top — the LAST matching entry
# wins. Today the project has a single maintainer so the catch-all
# is the only rule; add more specific patterns above it if scope
# gets divided in the future (e.g. `/.github/ @team-ci`).
